<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>كالرافع <span class="c2">(قدمه)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(في)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> النار <span class="c2">((وواضعها)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> في النار) <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
